rkarma.php?u=2060840)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ahbonjour" >ahbonjour</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;I'm so cold, Mama. Where are you? Where did you go? Mama!&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>4.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4120">SCP-4120</a> &quot;A good boy&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=7061118&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=7061118)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;SCP-4120 shows a desire to engage with human subjects&#8212;&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>5.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5380">SCP-5380</a> &quot;My world&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6394107&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="chiifu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6394107)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" >chiifu</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p><em>&quot;…And then, you became my World.&quot;</em></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><strong>6.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4242">SCP-4242</a> &quot;Foundations&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="WrongJohnSilver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" >WrongJohnSilver</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p><strong>&lt; POI-4242-𐤀 remains impassive. Tears begin to fall down his cheeks. &gt;</strong></p> </blockquote> <p><strong>7.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5807">SCP-5807</a> &quot;Pelicans Three&quot; by <span class="error-inline"><em>Magic8Ball04</em> 不匹配任何一个现有的用户名</span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Unlike you, I care for the safety, and what's more, the hope of my brothers.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>8.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2402">SCP-2402</a> &quot;That Takes Me Back&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="WrongJohnSilver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" >WrongJohnSilver</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;But when I dream, I do.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>9.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1281">SCP-1281</a> &quot;The Harbinger&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dreverettmann" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=323946&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="DrEverettMann" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=323946)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dreverettmann" >DrEverettMann</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;But a universe with voices saying &quot;I am here&quot; is far greater than a universe silent. One voice is small, but the difference between zero and one is as great as one and infinity.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>10.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4918">SCP-4918</a> &quot;<em>Bergentruckung</em>&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;I told him I was the Earl of Sussex as a joke. I thought he was going to take off my head—</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>he does not appreciate the Saxons.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><strong>11.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1958">SCP-1958</a> &quot;Magic Bus&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smapti" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=362048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Smapti" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=362048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smapti" >Smapti</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Blastoff! First men in space!&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>12.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1348">SCP-1348</a> &quot;Inner Sanctum&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ophite" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=354957&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="ophite" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=354957)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ophite" >ophite</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Dr. ██████: No. It's not ritual. No, it's not. Ben, you need to trust me on this.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>13.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1762">SCP-1762</a> &quot;Where The Dragons Went&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oz-ouroboros" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1743859&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="OZ Ouroboros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1743859)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oz-ouroboros" >OZ Ouroboros</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;We once filled each other's heads with dreams and goals.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>14.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-3195">SCP-3195</a> &quot;The Fault in Our Star&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marcelles-raynes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5722579&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Marcelles_Raynes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5722579)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marcelles-raynes" >Marcelles_Raynes</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p><strong>SCP-3195:</strong> Here's to bad moms.</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><strong>Dr. Rowe:</strong> To bad moms.</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>15.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1522">SCP-1522</a> &quot;Ships That Pass In The Night&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flameshirt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1467808&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="FlameShirt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1467808)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flameshirt" >FlameShirt</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p><em>Not all ships have to pass in the night.</em></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><strong>16.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4459">SCP-4459</a> &quot;The Ringmaster's Crown&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p><strong>SCP-4459:</strong> If I were to choose but a single word, Dr. Stewart, that word would undoubtedly be &quot;loss&quot;.</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>17.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-3385">SCP-3385</a> &quot;The Last Voyage of the Far Horizon.&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;We built this ship out of hope.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>18.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2123">SCP-2123</a> &quot;I Accidentally the Whole Universe&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/waterfire" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1672816&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Waterfire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1672816)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/waterfire" >Waterfire</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p><em>But here we are. You found enough to come to your current conclusion, consciously or otherwise. You’re sitting down in a private room and reading this text. Now is the time for answers.</em></p> </blockquote> <p><strong>19.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2605">SCP-2605</a> &quot;Caretaker&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zolgamax" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1707551&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Zolgamax" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1707551)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zolgamax" >Zolgamax</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Sing that song again, dear. The one I liked.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>20.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2583">SCP-2583</a> &quot;Dust to Dust&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drewbear" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=301632&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Drewbear" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=301632)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drewbear" >Drewbear</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;SCP-2583 separates the remains of these humanoid structures and does not reuse the dust.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><strong>21.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5520">SCP-5520</a> &quot;The Rabbit Hole&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" >HarryBlank</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;That, and nothing besides. You and I are the sum of our electro-chemical reactions. Electricity is the fire that is our conscious selves, and chemistry is the beating of our hearts.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>22.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5805">SCP-5805</a> &quot;You Can't Go Back&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeats" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2104082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="ManyMeats" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2104082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/manymeat