;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Ellie3" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3656445)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ellie3" >Ellie3</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Excuse me, I'm just waiting for a… a friend.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>35.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2420">SCP-2420</a> &quot;A Good Dog&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1345012&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="kinchtheknifeblade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1345012)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" >kinchtheknifeblade</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;I miss her so much. I didn't even get to tell her how good a girl she was. For, you know. Being magic.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><strong>36.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5971">SCP-5971</a> &quot;A Moment Where Words Don't Reach&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" >RockTeethMothEyes</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;I'm just there trying to do what I can, you know?&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>37.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-3511">SCP-3511</a> &quot;Reach Out And Touch&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>I asked her to move but she looked at me and said “Notice me. I want to be here. I want to be seen. I want to be touched. So no, you move me.”</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>38.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1424">SCP-1424</a> &quot;Patches&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/faminepulse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4275444&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="faminepulse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4275444)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/faminepulse" >faminepulse</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;SCP-1424 was discovered at an animal shelter in Los Angeles, California, following multiple failed euthanasia attempts.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>39.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1230">SCP-1230</a> &quot;A Hero is Born&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpixel" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1350583&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="MrPixel" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1350583)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpixel" >MrPixel</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;As sweet as dreams may be, eventually we all have to wake up.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>40.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1252">SCP-1252</a> &quot;A Half-Formed Idea&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" >SoullessSingularity</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Could you find her and tell her I'm okay? We got separated in an accident and I don't want her to worry.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><strong>41.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1342">SCP-1342</a> &quot;To the Makers of Music&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flameshirt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1467808&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="FlameShirt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1467808)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flameshirt" >FlameShirt</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;From one maker of music to another-&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>42.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4974">SCP-4974</a> &quot;The Mouse SCP&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" >Tanhony</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-4974 is an anomalous organism aesthetically identical to the character of Pikachu from the Pokémon media franchise.</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>Warning: this is not a nice trip down memory lane/of nostalgia.</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>43.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1960">SCP-1960</a> &quot;Neptunian Text Messages&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tiger66261" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1373135&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Tiger66261" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1373135)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tiger66261" >Tiger66261</a></span> rewritten by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smapti" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=362048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Smapti" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=362048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smapti" >Smapti</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Recurring themes in SCP-1960 communications include feelings of fear, isolation, and discomfort.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>44.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1166">SCP-1166</a> &quot;Perfect Lab Specimen&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2203795&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Kalinin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2203795)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" >Kalinin</a></span> (Original account deleted as seen in the articles history, found this in Helen her metadata.)</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-1166: (written response) Foundation makes dokter ██████ stop hurting we. foundation not hu8rt we?</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>Dr. ████████: I am not going to hurt you SCP-1166.</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>45.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2516">SCP-2516</a> &quot;The Man from Taured&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dododevil" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1854139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="DodoDevil" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1854139)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dododevil" >DodoDevil</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Yeah, how long are you going to keep me locked up in here? I’ve got a family waiting for me.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><strong>46.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5117">SCP-5117</a> &quot;<span style="color: red">Alex?</span> I’m Lonely&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greyve" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4045981&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Greyve" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4045981)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greyve" >Greyve</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;you can not leave me I am lonely all I am is loneliness and I know you know lonely because you are lonely and loneliness is all I am&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>47.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4361">SCP-4361</a> &quot;Red is Her Favorite Color&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kybard" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5717239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="Kybard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5717239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kybard" >Kybard</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;not cries for help. Cries to stop&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>48.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4686">SCP-4686</a> &quot;Hugs 4 Everyone&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/allerarey" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4386350&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="AlleraRey " style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4386350)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/allerarey" >AlleraRey</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;I really needed that. Thanks.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>49.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4274">SCP-4274</a> &quot;The Lonely Angel&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crystalmonarch" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2951031&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="CrystalMonarch" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2951031)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crystalmonarch" >CrystalMonarch</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;He may think himself alone on this world of ours but he can still see it's beauty. And so long as he can find the strength to continue, so can I.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>50.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5975">SCP-5975</a> &quot;The Cycle Keeps Spinning&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weizhong" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1777811&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="weizhong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1777811)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weizhong" >weizhong</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;<em>I miss you. I really, really miss you. I know why we have to stay in isolation but…I still really miss you.</em>&quot;</p> </blockquote> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <h1><span>其他</span></h1> <div id="wiki-tabview-d5d58ebe5029a2dc300ec43d5cdde8b0" class="yui-navset"> <ul class="yui-nav"> <li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>Format-Screw</em></a></li> </ul> <div class="yui-content"> <div id="wiki-tab-0-0"> <p>全部扭曲颠覆后的 SCP 格式趣味呈现法。</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;展开</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;隐藏</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2521">SCP-2521</a> &#8212; ●●|●●●●●|●●|● by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lurkd" >LurkD</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>维基最火 meta 系文档！该类文档绝赞入坑之作！全彩图。</p> </blockquote> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3999">SCP-3999</a> &#8212; 我于万物之中 by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" >LordStonefish</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>如果您想知道为什么这个清单中的大多数 SCP 都来自于系列 IV，这就是一个范例。SCP-3999 表明了一篇标准 SCP 与高质量写作差了有多远。满是杂乱无章的逻辑和杂言乱语。在这一点有争议。</p> </blockquote> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3043">SCP-3043</a> &#8212; 吕墨非于……3043的——奇案！ by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" >The Great Hippo</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>事<strong>吕墨非</strong>！从题材上来讲，一般的 SCP 条目应有分析性及科学性。现在来看看格式破坏后的 SCP 是个什么样！</p> </blockquote> <p><a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3972">SCP-3972</a> &#8212; &quot;Ken Burns Presents: SCP-3972&quot; by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kate-mctiriss" >Kate McTiriss</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>“第一个想到把视频融入文章的人，这是一大里程碑，而且值得把这个方法继续沿用下去。如果放到维基外面去，评分绝对能飚到十亿个 upvote 。记住我的话！”—— DjKaktus 。3972 没有十亿个 up，但的确把视频格式运用得很棒。</p> </blockquote> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3939">SCP-3939</a> &#8212; [编号保留，以待研究员] by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" >Croquembouche</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>还记得小时候读的冒险故事书吗！就是它！试试多看几遍呀。</p> </blockquote> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2439">SCP-2439</a> &#8212; [编号未分配] by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jack-ike" >Jack Ike</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>2016年D级竞赛并列冠军！如果想再好好读一遍，那就复制粘贴塞进空白文档里。</p> </blockquote> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3211">SCP-3211</a> &#8212; 一无二随 by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" >Croquembouche</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>一上来就完全颠覆你的认知，做好准备。</p> </blockquote> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2786">SCP-2786</a> &#8212; 原型 by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/billith" >Billith</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>很多 SCP 都会在不同迭代里变化，但这个由于执行命令的有效性而脱颖而出。</p> </blockquote> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3626">SCP-3626</a> &#8212; 不要停止阅读文档 by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kemot01" >kemoT01</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>和3211很像，这个 SCP 需要读者做出一个承诺：你只需要不停地阅读文档。</p> </blockquote> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3309">SCP-3309</a> &#8212; 化为泡影之时，我们去往何方 by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span> and <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/phamtomguy" >PhamtomGuy</a></span></p> <blockquote> <p>形而上学是一个常见的概念，在一个虚构的叙事层中赋予人物以意识，并且让他们意识到一个上层叙事正影响着他们的一举一动，就像影响一个真正存在的意识。读完了记得留条评论。</p> </blockquote> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ssssssz" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4608911&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248389" alt="ssssssz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4608911)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ssssssz" >ssssssz</a></span></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">脚注</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-96137-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>目前Reddit被墙，未搬运的内容无法打开。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-96137-2"><a href="javascript:;" >2</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>“细思恐极的故事”原文为 fridge horror ，是一种恐怖类型。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-96137-3"><a href="javascript:;" >3</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>TV Tropes可翻译成“剧情函数库”，是一个收集并扩大各项公约和在创意作品中发现的比喻说明和示例的维基百科网站，说白了就是用理工科的思维将各种影视作品解刨成单独的桥段的网站。Fridge horror可理解为一种桥段的总称。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-96137-4"><a href="javascript:;" >4</a>. <strong>译注：</strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-6012310/user-curated-lists#post-4142322">原文在此</a>。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-96137-5"><a href="javascript:;" >5</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>此句非出自原译文。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-96137-6"><a href="javascript:;" >6</a>. <strong>译注：</strong>此句非出自原译文。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-96137-7"><a href="javascript:;" >7</a>. 此处空出一个够长的地方，除了第一个字母（M）外其他字母为空</div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
